               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>U-cort<sup>®</sup> (Hydrocortisone Acetate Cream USP, 1%) is supplied in a 1 oz (28.35 g) (NDC 51672-3009-2) tube.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20200131"/>
               <component>
