                     <code code="44425-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="STORAGE AND HANDLING SECTION"/>
                     <text>
                        <paragraph>Store at 20° to 25°C (68° to 77°F) [see USP Controlled Room Temperature]. Protect from freezing.</paragraph>
                        <paragraph>
